9. Qe2 b6 10. Rd1 {This is the idea of this Bc4 system. The rook is going to
be very annoying from the d1 square.} Bb7 11. Ne5 {Principle of maximum
activity...} Qc8 12. Bg5 {All White's pieces are very active and Black hasn't
played c5 yet.} c5 13. c3 Qc7 14. dxc5 bxc5 (14... Qxc5 {Was probably a better
